OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FCare Minister Stephen Kinnock told ITV
OL,8,FNews the government will consider
OL,9,Famending mental health legislation
OL,10,Fcurrently going though Parliament, as
OL,11,FPolitical Correspondent Romilly Weeks
OL,12,Freports
OL,14,FThe government is considering changing
OL,15,Fthe law to give families the right to
OL,16,Frequest a mental capacity assessment
OL,17,Ffor a vulnerable loved one, ITV News
OL,18,Fcan reveal.
