OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FCare Minister Stephen Kinnock held a
OL,8,Fmeeting with cross-party MPs and Fiona
OL,9,FLaskaris, a mother who has spent years
OL,10,Ffighting for the change in law that
OL,11,Fshe believes could have saved her
OL,12,Fautistic son.
OL,14,FChristopher Laskaris was 24 years old
OL,15,Fwhen he was murdered in 2016 by a
OL,16,Fconvicted criminal who had been
OL,17,Fexploiting him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/23
