OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FFiona was repeatedly dismissed for
OL,8,Fyears when she tried to get her son a
OL,9,Fmental capacity assessment, which
OL,10,Festablishes whether someone has the
OL,11,Fability to make decisions about their
OL,12,Fown safety and wellbeing, and helps
OL,13,Fdetermine what support they may need.
OL,15,F"The law as it stands didn't enable me
OL,16,Fto save my son's life, even though I'd
OL,17,Fbeen asking for a proper mental
OL,18,Fcapacity assessment. There was no
OL,19,Fmechanism for me to do that," Fiona
OL,20,Fsaid ahead of the meeting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
