OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,F"So we want to change that. We've got
OL,8,Fa good amendment lined up and I think
OL,9,Fit'll probably work. I really, really
OL,10,Fhope the government will support
OL,11,Fgetting this amendment through so that
OL,12,Fno one else has to go through what we
OL,13,Fhave."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/23
