OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FSince ITV News aired Fiona's story and
OL,8,Fthe prime minister's subsequent pledge
OL,9,Fin the Commons to "look into" the law
OL,10,Fchange, we have been contacted by
OL,11,Fother families also battling to get
OL,12,Fmental capacity assessments. Due to
OL,13,Fthe issue being underreported, many
OL,14,Fsaid they didn't realise they were not
OL,15,Falone in their fight.
OL,17,FOne mother said she "sobbed
OL,18,Funcontrollably", adding: "I thought,
OL,19,Fthere are other people like us."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/23
