OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FIf you have been affected by this
OL,8,Fissue, you can contact
OL,9,Fyourstory@itv.com
OL,11,FFollowing the meeting on Wednesday,
OL,12,FCare Minister Kinnock told ITV News
OL,13,Fthe government will now consider
OL,14,Famending mental health legislation
OL,15,Fcurrently going though Parliament.
OL,17,FHe said: "Mrs Laskaris has absolutely
OL,18,Fmade her points - we absolutely see
OL,19,Fwhere she's coming from. Officials
OL,20,Fwill be now taking forward those
OL,21,Fdiscussions in greater detail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/23
