OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,F"Mrs Laskaris has proposed an
OL,8,Famendment to the bill. We will
OL,9,Fabsolutely be examining that in
OL,10,Fgreater detail, looking at the purpose
OL,11,Fof the amendment, but also what effect
OL,12,Fit might have just to ensure that
OL,13,Fthere aren't unintended consequences."
OL,15,F'Losing a child is the worst thing
OL,16,Fthat can happen to anyone, but I think
OL,17,Fa preventable death is the very
OL,18,Fworst,' Fiona Laskaris previously told
OL,19,FITV News.
