OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FWhat is the Mental Capacity Act and
OL,8,Fhow could the law change?
OL,10,FThe Mental Capacity Act was introduced
OL,11,Fin 2005 in a bid to minimise the
OL,12,Fnumber of vulnerable adults being
OL,13,Fdetained unreasonably and
OL,14,Findefinitely, and to give them more
OL,15,Fautonomy over their own care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
