OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FIt states that as a starting point
OL,8,Feveryone should be presumed to have
OL,9,Fthe capacity to make their own
OL,10,Fdecisions about their own safety and
OL,11,Fwellbeing, and that assessment should
OL,12,Fbe carried out if their capacity is in
OL,13,Fdoubt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/23
