OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FFiona and three MPs - the former
OL,8,Fhealth secretary Jeremy Hunt
OL,9,F(Conservatives), Chris Coghlan (Lib
OL,10,FDems) and Jake Richards (Labour) - are
OL,11,Fcalling for an amendment to the Mental
OL,12,FCapacity Act to ensure family members'
OL,13,Fviews are taken into account when
OL,14,Fdeciding if someone needs a mental
OL,15,Fcapacity assessment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/23
