OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FThey, along with the National Autistic
OL,8,FSociety, agree the current system is
OL,9,Ffailing autistic adults like
OL,10,FChristopher, as well as other adults
OL,11,Fwith learning disabilities and mental
OL,12,Fhealth illnesses - at times with
OL,13,Fcatastrophic consequences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/23
