OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FThey are concerned there are
OL,8,Fpotentially hundreds of preventable
OL,9,Fdeaths per year due to this issue,
OL,10,Fwith recent research finding The
OL,11,FMental Capacity Act was not followed
OL,12,Fin a quarter of the deaths of autistic
OL,13,Fpeople and those with learning
OL,14,Fdisabilities in 2022 alone.
OL,16,FBarrister Ian Brownhill, who's a
OL,17,Fspecialist in mental capacity, said
OL,18,Fdecisions around capacity are a
OL,19,Fproblem the courts see time and again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/23
