OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,F"The issues are vast," he said.
OL,8,F"Sometimes it can be something like a
OL,9,Fpredatory marriage where somebody
OL,10,Ftargets someone because they want to
OL,11,Fget access to their finances. In other
OL,12,Fcases it's more insipid - it might be
OL,13,Fsomething like a drug dealer, or
OL,14,Fcuckooing, and things like that.
OL,16,F"All of these issues start to come to
OL,17,Fthe fore. And one of the key issues in
OL,18,Fthem is whether or not that person has
OL,19,Fthe mental capacity to make a variety
OL,20,Fof different decisions for themselves
OL,21,Fin their life."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/23
