OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,F"They were assuming he's got capacity
OL,8,Fand therefore, it's his reasoned
OL,9,Fdecision - if he doesn't want help, he
OL,10,Fdoesn't want support, that's fine by
OL,11,Fus," she said.
OL,13,F"Even though I was providing evidence
OL,14,Fthat that's not the case. He's not
OL,15,Fwell. He doesn't understand the
OL,16,Fconsequences of this. There's no way
OL,17,Fon earth he would just lie in bed day
OL,18,Fand night like this deteriorating of
OL,19,Fhis own choice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
