OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,F"I genuinely believed that he would
OL,8,Fdie because he was just being left for
OL,9,Fmonths at a time with no support."
OL,11,FAsked how she felt when she heard
OL,12,FFiona's story, Parveen said: "I just
OL,13,Fcried uncontrollably because every
OL,14,Fquote I read, it was almost like I was
OL,15,Ftelling our story. Those very same
OL,16,Fthings about being dismissed as an
OL,17,Fover fussy parent - stop interfering,
OL,18,Fhe's an adult, he can make his own
OL,19,Fdecisions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
