OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,F"People would come in and see him in
OL,8,Fthis completely sick state - lying in
OL,9,Fhis bed withering away into this tiny
OL,10,Fform - but they wouldn't do anything."
OL,12,FShe added: "As I was reading this
OL,13,F(Fiona's) story... I thought, there
OL,14,Fare other people like us. This tragedy
OL,15,Fhas happened and services could've
OL,16,Fstopped this from happening. Fiona had
OL,17,Fraised this time and time again, like
OL,18,FI have over 12 years for my son."
