OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FCoghlan said: "We feel we need to see
OL,8,Fit in legislation because only then
OL,9,Fwill lives be saved. And frankly,
OL,10,FFiona's family hopefully can then
OL,11,Ffinally start the grieving process and
OL,12,Ffeel that some small piece of hope has
OL,13,Fcome out of what happened."
OL,15,FAsked what it would mean to her if the
OL,16,Flaw was passed, Fiona said: "Oh, it
OL,17,Fwould just mean so much to know other
OL,18,Fpeople wouldn't have to go through
OL,19,Fthis."
