OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsidering changing Mental Capacity
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FAfter years of fighting for justice
OL,8,Ffor her son's death, Fiona said she
OL,9,Ffinally feels like her voice is being
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,F"It's incredibly cathartic for me -
OL,13,Fjust being listened to. Shouldn't be
OL,14,Flike that though, it shouldn't take
OL,15,Feight years and an ITV crew to just
